_header: Prince duke and earl lord knight and squire
_description: James Ryman, a welcome to Christmas — one stanza rhyme royal

CULEe112.First Lines:
Prince duke & erle lord knyght & squierWith alle other in
                    youre degree…
CULEe112.Last Lines:
…That now was borne for loue of vsOf mayde mary named
                    Ihesus
